{"tid":984598,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"探射燈：電子暖蛋淪流動炸彈 高溫可致灼傷","createTime":"2019-01-17T02:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T02:59:47.000Z","uid":56881,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6c0acc2bc3d0a1f637f1af0d3748603f6b3b8908","tid":984598,"uid":56881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:39:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8E%A2%E5%B0%84%E7%87%88%EF%BC%9A%E9%9B%BB%E5%AD%90%E6%9A%96%E8%9B%8B%E6%B7%AA%E6%B5%81%E5%8B%95%E7%82%B8%E5%BD%88%E3%80%80%E9%AB%98%E6%BA%AB%E5%8F%AF%E8%87%B4%E7%81%BC%E5%82%B7-225815235.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%258E%25A2%25E5%25B0%2584%25E7%2587%2588%25EF%25BC%259A%25E9%259B%25BB%25E5%25AD%2590%25E6%259A%2596%25E8%259B%258B%25E6%25B7%25AA%25E6%25B5%2581%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2582%25B8%25E5%25BD%2588%25E3%2580%2580%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%25BA%25AB%25E5%258F%25AF%25E8%2587%25B4%25E7%2581%25BC%25E5%2582%25B7-225815235.html&d=ENjt5TdXBxjpftf5WjULUEjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=1338f92e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%8E%A2%E5%B0%84%E7%87%88%EF%BC%9A%E9%9B%BB%E5%AD%90%E6%9A%96%E8%9B%8B%E6%B7%AA%E6%B5%81%E5%8B%95%E7%82%B8%E5%BD%88%E3%80%80%E9%AB%98%E6%BA%AB%E5%8F%AF%E8%87%B4%E7%81%BC%E5%82%B7-225815235.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4nZqWkMoq8Uc.FwfDQTR0w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/0c55b0f3d92cfba682881eab5916358a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F4nZqWkMoq8Uc.FwfDQTR0w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM1%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2F0c55b0f3d92cfba682881eab5916358a&h=6dc94543&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n理大電機工程學系團隊為各樣本充電後，量度其表面及電池最高溫度，並同時檢測持續釋出熱力時間，發現全部電池溫度都超過攝氏40度的安全標準，其中樣本一更達攝氏62.6度，比安全標準高逾56%；樣本二及三的電池溫度都超過攝氏52度，超標30%，樣本四則為攝氏46.6度。暖蛋表面的最高溫度則錄得約攝氏44度至55度不等，可維持熱力的時間介乎76至184分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n理大電機工程學系教授鄭家偉指，樣本一屬非常危險水平，不當使用有可能爆炸，而且其表面溫度亦高達攝氏55度，「應該要搵啲嘢隔住先好掂，徒手接觸好易灼傷。」其中3個樣本都使用鋰電池，拆開表面後發覺其內部焊口粗糙，電池與發熱體的距離過近，只隔了一層膠，可導致過熱損壞，加上鋰電池全部未有排氣口及防護裝置，一旦爆開會導致用者受傷。<br />\n<br />\n此外，樣本四可更換即棄電池，但同時設有USB插頭可供充電，鄭提醒若不為意裝進即棄鹼性電池而又再以插頭充電的話，有可能令電池爆開，增加風險。<br />\n<br />\n樣本的包裝說明與檢測結果亦不乎，風險最高的樣本一包裝盒上印有「安全永不爆炸」的字句；而樣本二聲稱表面熱力可達攝氏50度及55度，但檢測結果只有約攝氏44度。<br />\n<br />\n香港仲有冬天架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab78dcf3537eb34b4fad4b078da41515eb2188e2","tid":984598,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:42:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bdde121ca77be8d61db6d6421566862a50146b5c","tid":984598,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:55:01.000Z","msg":"使唔使用暖蛋呀"},{"pid":"6599e91c6d84f2b4377065970afaf6b573e2fe36","tid":984598,"uid":226156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab78dcf3537eb34b4fad4b078da41515eb2188e2","tid":984598,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:42:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T02:59:47.000Z","msg":"你教唆販賣殺傷力武器俾港獨人士，你仆街喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}